name: Toonify - Legacy Model
description:
Legacy Toon Model

See Credits Below.

I enjoyed experimenting with this mix and didn't like that it was nuked off the internet leaving me with only a local copy for backup.

Already pruned / fp16 / safetensor, did not modify this at all.

Note:

This was an earlier version of https://civitai.com/models/36281/toonify - called "Toonify 2.0".

They are not the same model / mix.

Prompting Info

  • Pretty simple to use

  • Clip 1 & Clip 2 both work, try them out

  • If you put in prompts like 'illustrated' or 'high def' you can push this model to be more detailed.. but that sort of defeats the point

  • I don't show this in any of the samples.. but because of the super clean line work and color palette, you can mix this with a lot of different LORA's and get some cool stuff.


Recommended Negative Prompt (Not Strict - Experiment):

worst quality, low quality:1.4), easynegative, bad-hands-5,
